'o Noteooks section allows you to create Jupyter Noteooks, copy sample'
'noteooks, and run noteooks and Python scripts.'
'o Automated ML steps you through creating a machine learning model without'
'writing code.'
'\xc2\x7 Designer gives you a drag-and-drop way to uild models using preuilt'
'components.'
'.'
'The Assets section of the studio helps you keep track of the assets you create as'
"you run your jos. If you have a new workspace, there's nothing in any of these"
'sections yet.'
'\xc2\x7 You already used the Manage section of the studio to create your compute'
'resources. This section also lets you create and manage data and external services'
'you link to your workspace.'
